       <p id="u14821-9"><span id="u14821-7">Location: </span>Amberley, West Sussex</p>
       <p id="u14821-12"><span id="u14821-10">Venue: </span>Newnham Park, Plympton, Plymouth, PL7 5BN</p>
       <p id="u14821-15"><span id="u14821-13">Registration Opens: </span>7:30am</p>
       <p id="u14821-18"><span id="u14821-16">Start Time: </span>7.45am - 9:30am</p>
       <p id="u14821-21"><span id="u14821-19">Entry on Day:</span> Yes, if the event is not sold out.</p>
       <p id="u14821-22">&nbsp;</p>
       <p id="u14821-24">Local Transportation</p>
       <p id="u14821-26">Public transportation is limited to the area, and a rental car is recommended and all major rental agencies are</p>
       <p id="u14821-28">available locally and at both airports. Rush hour traffic can double or triple driving times, especially on Fridays.</p>
       <p id="u14821-30">Please plan accordingly.</p>
